reviewText: Yay! Petit Ours Brun playable on a US DVD player ! So fun!
Super, me fille adore. Les petites histoires sont parfaites pour son age (2 ans) J'ai recu le DVD dans les temps et en bonne condition. Fonctionne parfaitement.

Was suprised that the turtles I ordered were not the ones I received...after contacting the seller I learned an error was made and I was sent a different turtle they make. My daughter is happy with these so we will keep them. Seller responded with a kindly e-mail admitting his error and was happy to have corrected it. Overall product is nice and just what we needed to frame a corner of a beach poster.
